text: Farm "Welgelegen" in Willeskop Willeskop is a village in the Dutch province of Utrecht. It is located in the municipality of Montfoort, 2 km east of that city. Willeskop was a separate municipality between 1818 and 1989, when it was merged with Montfoort. ==References== ==External links== * Map of the former municipality in 1868.
